PRIVACY POLICY
To protect your personal information, CJ Olive Young Corporation(hereafter, ‘Olive Young’) complies with any applicable law such as 「the Personal Information Protection Act (PIPA)」 and 「the Act on Promotion of Information and communications Network Utilization and Information Protection」, General Data Protection Regulation(GDPR) etc.
Olive Young strives to prevent the leakage and damage of your personal information.
