Article 1 (Purpose of Collecting and Processing Personal Information)
1. Olive Young collects only basic personal information necessary to provide its services, and seeks your consent when collecting additional information for services tailored to your tastes and interests.
If you are a registered user, not providing optional information will not restrict your use of services.
If you are not a registered user, you may refuse to give your consent, in which case you will not able to purchase items at Olive Young.
2. Olive Young does not collect any sensitive personal information such as your race or ethnicity, religion and philosophical beliefs, country of origin, political opinions, criminal record, medical information, and sexual orientation.
